  "locationId": "ship_deck",
  "locationName": "Ship's Deck",
  "imageDescription": "A weathered pirate ship deck under overcast skies, with coiled ropes, wooden barrels, and brass fittings gleaming despite the salt corrosion. The mainmast towers overhead with furled sails, while the harbor stretches beyond the gunwale. Fantasy art style, detailed digital illustration.",
  "musicDescription": "Atmospheric sea shanty with creaking wood, distant gulls, and gentle waves lapping against the hull, building tension with minor key undertones suggesting mystery and danger.",
